    <p>As an esteemed multidisciplinary creator, Ben Banker joins us at the 0x888 Agency as our featured artist. Banker originates from the city of Chicago and currently resides in Madison, Wisconsin. He has earned a Bachelor of Fine Arts degree from the prestigious School of the Art Institute of Chicago, along with over two decades of experience in both traditional painting and digital art.</p>
    <p>Banker's love for art has taken him on extensive travels across the United States, Canada, and Europe, where he has sought to immerse himself in the vast cultural offerings of world-class museums and galleries. It was during his time at the Art Institute of Chicago, however, that Banker was able to hone his skills and studied the masters up close, spending countless hours pouring over paintings with a discerning eye.</p>
    <p>With his inherent talent for web design and digital art, Banker has embraced the rapidly growing phenomenon of AI art and the exciting new frontiers of the NFT realm. His work continues to push the boundaries of what is possible while staying true to his artistic vision.</p>
